{
  "page": "List of actors of A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>This page is intended to list the actors playing in the adapted televised series <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i>. This wiki is centered on the books and not the televised series, thus this article is not intended to provide exhaustive biographies or filmographies of the actors. If you seek that information follow the links; each entry is linked to the actor's Wikipedia page (if present) and to the Internet Movie Database (IMDb) entry devoted to the actor in question.\n</p>\n<div class=\"toclimit-2\"><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#A-O\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">A-O</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Bertie_Carvel.2C_Baelor_Targaryen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bertie Carvel, Baelor Targaryen</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Chloe_Lea.2C_Rafe\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chloe Lea, Rafe</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Connan_Aaron.2C_Gowen_Baratheon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Connan Aaron, Gowen Baratheon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Daniel_Ings.2C_Lyonel_Baratheon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Daniel Ings, Lyonel Baratheon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Daniel_Monks.2C_Manfred_Dondarrion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Daniel Monks, Manfred Dondarrion</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Danny_Webb.2C_Arlan_of_Pennytree\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Danny Webb, Arlan of Pennytree</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Dexter_Sol_Ansell.2C_Egg\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dexter Sol Ansell, Egg</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Edward_Ashley.2C_Steffon_Fossoway\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Edward Ashley, Steffon Fossoway</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Finn_Bennett.2C_Aerion_Targaryen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Finn Bennett, Aerion Targaryen</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Henry_Ashton.2C_Daeron_Targaryen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.10</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Henry Ashton, Daeron Targaryen</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#P-Z\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">P-Z</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Peter_Claffey.2C_Duncan_the_Tall\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Peter Claffey, Duncan the Tall</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Ross_Anderson.2C_Humfrey_Hardyng\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ross Anderson, Humfrey Hardyng</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#Sam_Spruell.2C_Maekar_Targaryen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sam Spruell, Maekar Targaryen</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-16\"><a href=\"#Shaun_Thomas.2C_Raymun_Fossoway\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Shaun Thomas, Raymun Fossoway</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-17\"><a href=\"#Steve_Wall.2C_Leo_Tyrell\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Steve Wall, Leo Tyrell</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-18\"><a href=\"#Tanzyn_Crawford.2C_Tanselle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tanzyn Crawford, Tanselle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-19\"><a href=\"#Tom_Vaughan-Lawlor.2C_Plummer\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tom Vaughan-Lawlor, Plummer</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-20\"><a href=\"#Wade_Briggs.2C_Roland_Crakehall\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wade Briggs, Roland Crakehall</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-21\"><a href=\"#Youssef_Kerkour.2C_Steely_Pate\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Youssef Kerkour, Steely Pate</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A-O\">A-O</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A-O\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span id=\"Bertie_Carvel,_Baelor_Targaryen\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bertie_Carvel.2C_Baelor_Targaryen\">Bertie Carvel, Baelor Targaryen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Bertie Carvel, Baelor Targaryen\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertie_Carvel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bertie Carvel\">Robert Hugh Carvel</a> is an English actor born 6 September 1977 in Marleybone, London. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen_(son_of_Daeron_II)\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen (son of Daeron II)\">Baelor Targaryen</a>. Carvel is known for <i>Jonathan Strange &amp; Mr Norrell</i>, <i>Doctor Foster</i>, <i>Matilda the Musical</i>, and <i>Ink</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1584487/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Chloe_Lea,_Rafe\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chloe_Lea.2C_Rafe\">Chloe Lea, Rafe</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Chloe Lea, Rafe\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Chloe Lea is a British actress born 4 November 2005 in Blackburn, England, who grew up in Swinton. She plays <a href=\"/index.php/Rafe\" title=\"Rafe\">Rafe</a> in flashback scenes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Lea is known for <i>Dune: Prophecy</i> and <i>Foundation</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm8049677/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Connan_Aaron,_Gowen_Baratheon\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Connan_Aaron.2C_Gowen_Baratheon\">Connan Aaron, Gowen Baratheon</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Connan Aaron, Gowen Baratheon\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Connan Aaron is an Irish actor. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Gowen_Baratheon\" title=\"Gowen Baratheon\">Gowen Baratheon</a>. Aaron was a stand-in for Kit Harington (<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>) in the final two seasons of <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Daniel_Ings,_Lyonel_Baratheon\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Daniel_Ings.2C_Lyonel_Baratheon\">Daniel Ings, Lyonel Baratheon</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Daniel Ings, Lyonel Baratheon\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Ings\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Ings\">Daniel Ings</a> is an English actor born 30 November 1985. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Baratheon\" title=\"Lyonel Baratheon\">Lyonel Baratheon</a>. Ings is known for <i>Lovesick</i>, <i>Black Mirror</i>, and <i>The Crown</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3958526/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Daniel_Monks,_Manfred_Dondarrion\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Daniel_Monks.2C_Manfred_Dondarrion\">Daniel Monks, Manfred Dondarrion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Daniel Monks, Manfred Dondarrion\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Monks\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Monks\">Daniel Monks</a> is an Australian actor and screenwriter. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Dondarrion\" title=\"Manfred Dondarrion\">Manfred Dondarrion</a>. He is known for <i>Pulse</i>, <i>Dead Hot</i>, and <i>In the Room Where He Waits</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3399361/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Danny_Webb,_Arlan_of_Pennytree\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Danny_Webb.2C_Arlan_of_Pennytree\">Danny Webb, Arlan of Pennytree</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Danny Webb, Arlan of Pennytree\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danny_Webb_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Danny Webb (actor)\">Daniel \"Danny\" Webb</a> is an English actor born 6 June 1958 in London. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_of_Pennytree\" title=\"Arlan of Pennytree\">Arlan of Pennytree</a>. Webb is known for <i>Alien 3</i>, <i>Henry VIII</i>, and <i>Doctor Who</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0916073/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Dexter_Sol_Ansell,_Egg\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dexter_Sol_Ansell.2C_Egg\">Dexter Sol Ansell, Egg</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Dexter Sol Ansell, Egg\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dexter_Sol_Ansell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dexter Sol Ansell\">Dexter Sol Ansell</a> is an English child actor born 16 September 2014. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>. Ansell is known for <i>The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds &amp; Snakes</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm11274700/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Edward_Ashley,_Steffon_Fossoway\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Edward_Ashley.2C_Steffon_Fossoway\">Edward Ashley, Steffon Fossoway</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Edward Ashley, Steffon Fossoway\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Ashley_(English_actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Edward Ashley (English actor)\">Edward Ashley</a> is an English actor. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a>. Ashley is known for <i>The Lost City of Z</i>, <i>The Terror</i>, and <i>Masters of the Air</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5361352/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Finn_Bennett,_Aerion_Targaryen\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Finn_Bennett.2C_Aerion_Targaryen\">Finn Bennett, Aerion Targaryen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Finn Bennett, Aerion Targaryen\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finn_Bennett\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Finn Bennett\">Finn Bennett</a> is an Irish-British actor born 1999. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion Targaryen</a>. Bennett is known for <i>True Detective: Night Country</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3882611/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Henry_Ashton,_Daeron_Targaryen\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Henry_Ashton.2C_Daeron_Targaryen\">Henry Ashton, Daeron Targaryen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Henry Ashton, Daeron Targaryen\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Henry Ashton is an actor. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>. Ashton is known for <i>A Good Girl's Guide to Murder</i>, <i>Outlander</i>, and <i>My Lady Jane</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12254475/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"P-Z\">P-Z</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: P-Z\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span id=\"Peter_Claffey,_Duncan_the_Tall\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Peter_Claffey.2C_Duncan_the_Tall\">Peter Claffey, Duncan the Tall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Peter Claffey, Duncan the Tall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Claffey\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Peter Claffey\">Peter Claffey</a> is an Irish actor and former rugby union player born 28 July 1996 in Portumna, County Galway. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a>. Claffey is known for <i>Harry Wild</i>, <i>Wreck</i>, and <i>Bad Sisters.</i> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12853749/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Ross_Anderson,_Humfrey_Hardyng\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ross_Anderson.2C_Humfrey_Hardyng\">Ross Anderson, Humfrey Hardyng</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Ross Anderson, Humfrey Hardyng\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ross Anderson is a Scottish actor born 15 July 1987 in Paisley, Renfrewshire. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a>. Anderson is known for <i>The Last Kingdom</i>, <i>The King's Man</i>, and <i>Crawl</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5105119/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Sam_Spruell,_Maekar_Targaryen\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sam_Spruell.2C_Maekar_Targaryen\">Sam Spruell, Maekar Targaryen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Sam Spruell, Maekar Targaryen\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Spruell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sam Spruell\">Sam Spruell</a> is an English actor born 1 January 1977 in Southwark, London. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maekar I Targaryen\">Maekar Targaryen</a>. Spruell is known for <i>Snow White and the Huntsman</i>, <i>Legend</i>, and <i>Taken 3</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0819874/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Shaun_Thomas,_Raymun_Fossoway\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Shaun_Thomas.2C_Raymun_Fossoway\">Shaun Thomas, Raymun Fossoway</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Shaun Thomas, Raymun Fossoway\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Shaun Thomas is an English actor born 30 May 1997 in Bradford, West Yorkshire. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Raymun_Fossoway\" title=\"Raymun Fossoway\">Raymun Fossoway</a>. He is known for <i>The Selfish Giant</i>, <i>The Brothers Grimsby</i>, and <i>How to Have Sex</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5649091/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Steve_Wall,_Leo_Tyrell\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Steve_Wall.2C_Leo_Tyrell\">Steve Wall, Leo Tyrell</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Steve Wall, Leo Tyrell\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Wall\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Steve Wall\">Stephen Patrick \"Steve\" Wall</a> is an Irish musician and actor born in Kingsbury, London, England. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(Longthorn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (Longthorn)\">Leo Tyrell</a>. Wall is known for <i>Dune: Part Two</i>, <i>The Witcher</i>, and <i>The English</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2425811/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Tanzyn_Crawford,_Tanselle\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tanzyn_Crawford.2C_Tanselle\">Tanzyn Crawford, Tanselle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Tanzyn Crawford, Tanselle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Tanzyn Crawford is an Australian actress born in Perth. She plays <a href=\"/index.php/Tanselle\" title=\"Tanselle\">Tanselle</a>. Crawford is known for <i>Servant</i>, <i>Tiny Beautiful Things</i>, and <i>Swift Street</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm10624980/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Tom_Vaughan-Lawlor,_Plummer\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tom_Vaughan-Lawlor.2C_Plummer\">Tom Vaughan-Lawlor, Plummer</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Tom Vaughan-Lawlor, Plummer\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Tom Vaughan-Lawlor is an Irish actor born 4 November 1977 in Dundrum, Dublin. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Plummer\" title=\"Plummer\">Plummer</a>. Vaughan-Lawlor is known for <i>Love/Hate</i>, <i>Avengers: Infinity War</i>, and <i>Avengers: Endgame</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2534167/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Wade_Briggs,_Roland_Crakehall\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wade_Briggs.2C_Roland_Crakehall\">Wade Briggs, Roland Crakehall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Wade Briggs, Roland Crakehall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wade Briggs is an Australian actor born in Melbourne, Victoria. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Crakehall_(Kingsguard)\" title=\"Roland Crakehall (Kingsguard)\">Roland Crakehall</a>. Briggs is known for <i>Foundation</i> and <i>His Dark Materials</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4178551/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Youssef_Kerkour,_Steely_Pate\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Youssef_Kerkour.2C_Steely_Pate\">Youssef Kerkour, Steely Pate</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Youssef Kerkour, Steely Pate\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Youssef_Kerkour\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Youssef Kerkour\">Youssef Kerkour</a> is a Moroccan-English actor. He plays <a href=\"/index.php/Steely_Pate\" title=\"Steely Pate\">Steely Pate</a>. Kerkour is known for <i>Home</i>. (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1454881/\">IMDb</a>)\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:AKOTSK\" title=\"Template:AKOTSK\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:AKOTSK&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:AKOTSK (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:AKOTSK&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nHBO's <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Hedge_Knight_(TV_episode)&amp;action=